  "purpose": "The group unites parliamentarians, organisations, and experts to address the UK’s fertility crisis. It champions equitable access to treatment, family-building, and legal recognition for all families, while advocating statutory fertility leave and protection from discrimination. Long-term goals include education, prevention, and proactive reproductive health policy reform nationwide.",
